  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Housekeeping Attendant / Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>ATTENTION</strong> independent free spirits who thrive on friendship, community and new experiences!</p><p><br /></p><p>M Social Singapore is characteristically scouting for the curious, the explorers and the ones who dare to dream. We lust sanguine individuals who are expressive with a touch of creativity. Leave the stiff handshakes behind. Let's make some memories together. Join our M Socialite movement.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wait no further, M Social Casting CALL - <strong>Housekeeping Attendant / Supervisor </strong>is now open!</p><p><br /></p><p>The role reports to the Executive Housekeeper and <strong>YOU</strong> are responsible for the following: -</p><ul><li>To prepare daily work assignment for Room Attendants</li><li>Supervise the activities of the Room Attendants to ensure that the guest rooms corridors & service areas are well maintained</li><li>Conduct daily inspection of rooms to ensure cleanliness is consistent with the brand standard</li><li>Supervise minibar sales and replenishment operations</li><li>Supervise uniforms and guests' laundry cleaning</li><li>To carry out any other duties and responsibilities as assigned</li><li>Kungfu Fighting (Just kidding!)</li></ul><p>So what's the requirements?</p><ul><li>Preferably with Diploma in Hospitality Management or equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years of experience in similar capacity, managing room attendants</li><li>Attentive to details</li><li>Good housekeeping knowledge in room and public area cleaning, chemicals and pest controls</li><li>Ability to train and supervise staff and communicate well with management and guests</li><li>Willing to work weekends and public holiday</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>JUST BE FUN & BE ALL READY TO MINGLE</strong> with at least 1 year experience in a similar capacity!</p><p><br /></p><p>Time and tide wait for no man, hurry send in your application NOW!</p><p><br /></p><p><em>We apologise that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</em></p>",
